title: Pleng Rak Chao Phraya
overview: A story of Tone Chaopraya, a handsome and lively young man who hailed from Phetchaburi to join a singing contest. He has a strong competition, Tubtim, a woman who escaped from an arranged marriage. However, a shootout happens during the competition when the police storm the place after hearing rumors that Ratcha-Angkoon, a swindling thief will be there to steal the prize money.
